.ie \n(.g .ds Aq \(aq
.el .ds Aq '
.TH init 1  "init " 
.SH NAME
init \- Initialize a new vault and generate a keypair
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBmurk init\fR [\fB\-\-vault\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Initialize a new vault and generate a keypair
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-vault\fR \fI<VAULT>\fR [default: .murk]
Vault filename
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
